    <sect3 role="installation">
      <title>Installation of Snowballstemmer</title>

    <para> Build the module: </para>

<screen><userinput>make dist_libstemmer_python</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      This package does not come with a test suite.
    </para>

    <para>
      Now, as the <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem> user:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>pip3 install --no-index --find-links dist --no-cache-dir --no-user snowballstemmer</userinput></screen>

